## 📝 How to Start

```bash
cd ~/-iot-pipeline/tools
./1-validate-and-up.sh
```

To shut down the stack:

```bash
./2-shutdown--clean.sh
```

To remove volumes (⚠️ Destroys data):

```bash
./3-clean-volumes-.sh
```

